  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IArc2, IArcString, ICurveSegment, IGenericCurve, ICurve, IOrientableCurve, IOrientablePrimitive, IPrimitive, IGeometry, Cloneable

    public class GM_Arc2
extends GM_CurveSegment
implements IArc2
    An oriented 2D arc segment, defined by its center, its radius, its start and end angles, and its direction This class is bot part of the OGC standard but is needed for some applications
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    julien Gaffuri

      • getInterpolation

        public String getInterpolation()
        Description copied from class: GM_CurveSegment
        Mécanisme d'interpolation, selon une liste de codes. Vaut "linear" par défaut.

        La liste de codes est la suivante : {linear, geodesic, circularArc3Points, circularArc2PointsWithBulge, elliptical, clothoid, conic, polynomialSpline, cubicSpline, rationalSpline}.
